Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.36,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:47.83,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 30 - Birthday Gifts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Finished it! Look, isn't it pretty, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:02.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little! Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Must be that he chased a butterfly or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:17.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, when I call, usually he'd return at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:24.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little! Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:29.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:31.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Little!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:38.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At last, a spring was here.\NAnd with it, Little also grew quite big.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:44.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been, Little? When I call for you,\Nyou must return at once, is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like he wants you to come along. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:51.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:55.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Little.\NWhere exactly do you want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There are some sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But why is it only two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to show up this sheep you found?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sit, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:33.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright, Madame Sheep.\NLittle won't do anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Must be that Mr. Long is somewhere in the vicinity. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:41.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't see any other sheep around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, those must be the lost sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:46.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's help them find Mr. Long's herd, Kate. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But... Where exactly could Mr. Long be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not too far from here, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:53.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Let's try looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Little is going that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, too, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on.\NYou two need to hurry, too. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Those are Mr. Long's dogs again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why are they barking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Must be that they sensed our smell. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:42.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:48.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, stick closely to me now. Okay? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:56.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget us, Monocle?\NIt's us - Lucy and Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:01.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, Little is the cause.\NHe's barking at Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:05.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't growl in response, Little.\NOkay, let's keep walking. Slowly, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:12.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange?\NThe dogs are making such a fuss over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:15.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Long doesn't seem\Nto keep them in check at all. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, very strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:24.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Long! Mr. Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:31.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though he left for somewhere,\Nleaving the sheep unchecked. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd he do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:35.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he isn't anywhere around, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:49.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If he gets in a fight with dogs,\Nhe'll be in dire straights!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Enough already, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can relax now, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder whose cabin this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's Mr. Long's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, do you suppose he could be inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:04.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's very strange. It's been so loud outside here,\Nbut he didn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try looking inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've a bad feeling about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright. Let's just enter together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:15.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:20.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mr. Long indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:32.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:34.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:41.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not dead yet, but I'm about to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, very sick. Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Since the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:55.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, let's go and get Dr. Deighton here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'll go find him at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you bringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:07:59.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd much appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And if you see Ben, bring Ben along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:07.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He'll probably also be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:16.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You two! Enough shadowing us already,\Nreturn to where the sheep are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:18.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little won't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's best if you stay here with Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also me back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in pain, Mr. Long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My head spins when I try to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I tried many times to walk,\Nbut would collapse immediately. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you've nothing to worry about now,\N'cause the doctor is on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:56.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lucy. I'm so glad you could find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I though nobody would ever come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was actually Little who found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little? Ah! The baby dingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He'd become quite big already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So that was what the dogs made all this fuss over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:13.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Little never had any intention\Nto hurt the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:15.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really struggling to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This would be my first doctor's examination in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:32.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I lived in England,\Nthere wasn't any doctor in our village,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:36.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,and naturally, I've not seen a single doctor\Nafter I came to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:39.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can assure you Dr. Deighton is an amazing doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if a bit of a drunkard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And why did you ask to bring Ben along?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if this doctor is as good as you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:52.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he'll be able to bring me back to feet\Nat a moment's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:54.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You'll get well in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:10:01.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, the sheep need to be herded\Nto where there's water, that's what I need Ben for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ben would be able to do that on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:08.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's oughta be.\NHe helped me with that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:11.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I still don't believe in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:18.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No-no, not that. In a dingo\Nthat's disinterested in sheep. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:29.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Right, right, right.\NYou're getting quite good with it, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:33.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here, the bandage is done. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd say good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please come again in two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:50.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:53.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, please come with me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's a sick person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The shepherd, Mr. Long fell very ill! 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:01.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you say Mr. Long?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, right. He wanted you to come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:11.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Even Mr. Long already knows\NI'm helping Doctor Deighton in his practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:14.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was for some other reason\Nthat he wanted you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:18.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So where exactly do we need to go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good, good, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer feel dizzy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:28.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like I'm fine now.\NBy the way, where's that guy Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting outside the cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to bring him inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'd rather come to the doorway to look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:36.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:38.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:52.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:59.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see! He even wags his tail like any other dog would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Also, he's so big now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:04.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:05.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:14.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Long! Mr. Long!\NHang on, Mr. Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,W-wait! Wait a moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! One last push, please! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:25.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No, impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely impossible. Ah, I can't take it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not Little, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:34.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor. Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:37.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:42.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, it was because you rushed us too much,\Nthat ever Doctor has foam at the mouth now! 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:52.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate was... spurring me... "Run! Run!"\NAnd I... I'm struggling to even just walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ben, my bag. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:05.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Long's illness\Nwasn't that of an easily curable kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:13.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,While he was recovering, Ben had to cover for him\Nand become a full-time shepherd himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:24.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, are you really making a cake today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:28.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's so surprising about a cake\Nwhen it's someone's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:32.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's the first birthday cake we're having\Never since we came to Australia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:38.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause I barely had any free time\Nfor making birthday cakes up until now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:40.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:44.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's so marvelous! A birthday cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:48.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you'll have to make do\Nwithout birthday presents for now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Our life here is a little hectic as well. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:53.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! I don't need no presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:56.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we'll have a cake, I won't need anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:06.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little! Little!\NWe'll be eating a cake tonight! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go for a walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:15.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have her carry half of our bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:28.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She seems especially exhilarated, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:31.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the scene she made\Nabout going shopping with us? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by that look,\Nshe totally wasn't studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:40.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, girls.\NGood job with the shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:42.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you solve all the arithmetic problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:46.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you carry this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:52.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me to carry it,\Nafter you left me behind while shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually heavier than it looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not carrying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Little, let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Something's definitely wrong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Very strange.\NWhere are you going, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Out for a short walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:18.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, Ben, you're home early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:24.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Mr. Long is finally recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:27.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So he dismissed me from the shepherd's job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:28.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What about that sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Long gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of your pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:34.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. He gave me the money as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:36.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted me to give this to Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:37.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:41.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was Little who found Mr. Long\Nwhile he was suffering from illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:42.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's kinda true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he wanted to repay that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:47.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Also, he said you don't see a dingo\Ndisinterested in sheep every day. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:52.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So if we keep them side by side, dingo and sheep\Nbecoming buddies oughta do for a very amusing sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds fun, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:58.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One couldn't think of a better present\Nfor Lucy on her birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:16:01.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? It's her birthday today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom had already started making a cake, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:10.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So we're finally in a position\Nwhere we can afford a proper birthday party again? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:14.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Clara both bought presents for her, in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:18.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, since this sheep is also a birthday present,\NI'll try to hide it somewhere until the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I'll hide it in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:40.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, Mr. Long recovered at a lightning speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:47.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd come by sooner or later to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:51.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that to say your job as a shepherd is concluded?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:56.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Starting tomorrow, I'll be joining my dad\Nfor the road construction job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Road construction, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:02.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're not having it easy, I see.\NBack in England, all you had to do was going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:08.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think dad deserves more sympathy. He came\Nto Australia just to end up being a road builder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:12.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see... It was in the first days of winter, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:16.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When Mr. Popple said he might just have a chance\Nto get his hands on the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:21.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping that this spring your whole family\Nwould already be able to move there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:24.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad never told anyone where it was. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't go very well, I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:31.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, hope your father\Nstarts cultivating the land soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:36.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here and there, in the fields,\Nthe wheat is growing green already. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how dad feels about seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:42.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,His life is meaningless here,\Nif he can't farm, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, look over there! It's a carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:11.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, what are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:14.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We went on a walk, so I figured\NI might as well show this place to Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:19.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's important that Little\Nalso knows his way through the area. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I also thought I should show him\Nhow many people are living here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what was Little's reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:26.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like he's been one bit surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:31.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, dad, isn't it about time\Nwe leave the worrying about Little behind? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:34.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't know anything for certain yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:38.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A wild animal like this\Nmight be perfectly well-behaved at one point,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:42.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,but at the very next one,\Nhis ferocious dingo blood might call out to him. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:42.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm heading straight to home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:56.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you've been to Colonel Light's\Nsurveying office right now, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:01.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought you'd be building roads all day again. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:04.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Not quite. There was something\NI wanted to learn at Colonel's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:07.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what "Hm" means!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:12.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Popple, it's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Good afternoon, Mr. Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I finally managed to obtain a carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:31.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you had any progress\Nin getting the land?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:36.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:41.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought. The agricultural land\Nhad been getting increasingly expensive lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:46.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hearing there's a great many of folk just like you,\Nwho came to Southern Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:50.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,seeking to cultivate the land,\Nbut couldn't get their hands on any.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:52.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:57.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the surveying continues and the government\Nwill eventually start selling the cheap land as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wonder if they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:02.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep sincerely believing this kind of thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:06.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,you might end up waiting in the line\Nto get the land for eternity, I reckon. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:07.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddy up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:47.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday.\NHere's a small present from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:00.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:03.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you find some little treasure\Nyou'd want to store in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:13.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, my gift today is a lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:16.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Long gave it to me,\Nin order to see Little and a sheep getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:20.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:22.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I put it in the enclosure with the goats.\NYou'll see it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:24.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Save your thanks for Mr. Long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:28.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:35.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, I told Lucy-May\Nthat she shouldn't expect to get any gifts today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:37.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And that she'd have to make do with just a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:40.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone ended up\Ngiving her such marvelous things!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:43.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm extremely delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, get to eating, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:55.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My? Do you mean to say you've prepared\Nsome give for Lucy-May too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:58.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I believe, Lucy-May will like it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:01.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But in fact, it's somewhat more of a gift\Nto our entire family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:02.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:05.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:11.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You need a vast space of land to run a farm on it...\NAnd I bought just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:19.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's marvelous. Marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:22.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:28.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At last, we'll be able to start a farm, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:29.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So when will it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:33.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll sign the official contract in the nearest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:37.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A certain Mr. Wilson agreed to yield his land to me,\Nas circumstances warrant his return to England.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:40.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great news, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:44.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The deal was exactly the sum\Nwe were prepared to fork over. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:49.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad. So glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:51.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to celebrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We finally caught the winds of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:55.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:10.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, little lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know you have a very beautiful fur?\NIt's so white!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:19.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided on your name - Snowflake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:26.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're here, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:28.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:31.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to present to you - Snowflake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:38.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You two should get along well, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:43.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A dingo and a sheep.\NI wonder if it's really possible for them to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:48.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's exactly the same\Nas if a cat and a mouse were getting along, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.58,0:23:52.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Today, Lucy turned eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.19,0:24:07.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As we were returning from our tour\Nto Mr. Wilson's farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:10.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, who we brought along\Nseems to be unable to calm down. 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:14.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"Little and the Black Dog".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.42,0:24:15.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
